# 🕹️ Tic-Tac-Toe AI (Unbeatable AI)  
This is an **AI-powered Tic-Tac-Toe game** where the AI is **unbeatable** using the **Minimax Algorithm**.  
Built with **Python & Tkinter**, this game provides a **GUI-based interface** for easy gameplay.  

---

## 📌 **Features**  
✅ **Graphical Interface (GUI)** – Built using **Tkinter**  
✅ **Unbeatable AI** – Uses **Minimax Algorithm**  
✅ **Click to Play** – No typing, just click on the board  
✅ **Restart Button** – Play multiple rounds easily  
✅ **Instant AI Move** – AI plays immediately after the user  

